# uncited-os runs fully locally and is preconfigured for the local Supabase
# stack in .env.development (started by ./up.sh). You normally do NOT need to
# create this file at all.
#
# Set any of these to customise; they override the defaults in .env.development.

# OpenAI key — enables semantic recommendations (For You / Discover / My Field)
# and paper summaries. You can also paste it in Settings -> Setup instead of
# putting it here. Without a key, uncited-os is a full RSS reader (Level 1).
# OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...

# Optional: Anthropic key for automatic article-type classification.
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...

# How often the background fetch refreshes followed journals, in hours (default 3).
# FETCH_INTERVAL_HOURS=3
